<title>
CVT Oil Pan Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5506020">CVT Oil Pan Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that no metal particle is attached to the oil cleaner magnets (1). If attached, clean them.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check CVT oil pan (2) for crack, deformation, and damage. Replace CVT oil pan if defective.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9D30P550027.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.055mm" ver = "01" gw = "146" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
